features: ELEGANT DESIGN - This tapestry adopts advanced HD print. Do not worry about fading. Vivid colors, crisp lines and delicate hemming, it will bring your room a more permanent harmonious decoration.
AMAZING MATERIAL - This tapestry is made of 100% polyester fabric, which is soft, durable, safety, lightweight and easy to hang or pack away for your indoor or outdoor use.
DIFFERENT AVAILABLE SIZE - Different sizes give you more choices for different usage scenarios.
WASH ATTENTION - Hand wash or machine wash with cold water, hang to dry, iron at low temperatures, please do not expose to the sun, do not bleach...
EASY USE & CARE - You can hang this tapestry with decorative tacks or push pins easily. Dry clean or gentle hand wash in cold water. You can also easily iron it on low temperature.
